0.0.1
=====

*   Parse commandline
*   Global options
    -   --foo --foo=bar --foo='bar goo' --foo="bar goo"
*   One command
*   Command specific options
    -   -foo -foo=bar -foo='bar goo' -foo="bar goo"
*   Map command directly to !new! public methods of subclass
*   default command

